\section{Case Study — Diffusion--Reaction / Materials Systems}

\subsection{Anchors, interpretation, and scope}
We adopt the Option~A normalization (rad/s; hats suppressed). The coherence field
$\Psi(\mathbf x,t)$ represents a smoothed order parameter (e.g., phase fraction,
normalized composition, or an effective microstructural envelope). The central
cadence $\Omega_0$ plays the role of a reference timescale associated with
